      • MetaOperation

        public MetaOperation(ExecutableElement element)
        Extracts data from the executable element to form the model. The annotations are not copied over as the resulting SLSB may not expect them and would cause problems (e.g. @Inject when there shouldn't be one).
        Parameters:
        element - the method to process
